[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/85/318540.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1504813","time":"2019-10-5 19:20","userId":"318540","userName":"mirrorside","userSign":"","message":"和我正好相反。。 自从毕业上班后根本没心思精力看动画 天天就拿手机看看漫画小说<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> 我的新番进度现在还停留在2018年。。。<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">里番倒是看的还蛮勤快</span><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">至于你说这些我在刚接触漫画时也有这些问题。。不过看多了就行了。。。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">可能还是没看习惯吧？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/42/69/426934.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1504829","time":"2019-10-5 19:31","userId":"426934","userName":"火龙果汁","userSign":"","message":"<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">本子看了很多，但是确实习惯不了</span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/16/27/162791.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1504887","time":"2019-10-5 21:29","userId":"wyxd","userName":"苇原雪道","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/55/325509.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1504818","time":"2019-10-5 19:22","userId":"325509","userName":"hgy0353","userSign":"(少年哟，你不必成为神话。)","message":"动画看多是这样的，分镜不和动画一样，字一密就很难读<br>动画化改的那种去读确实会感觉好一些<br><br>其次就是沉浸感，动画是被动，gal小说漫画需要主动推动剧情<br>动画的沉浸感来源声优卖力&特效bgm等声音带来的，不如尝试有声小说<br><br><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/63.gif\" smileid=\"102\" alt=\"(bgm86)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/42/69/426934.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1504830","time":"2019-10-5 19:33","userId":"426934","userName":"火龙果汁","userSign":"","message":"太难辽"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1504820","time":"2019-10-5 19:23","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"漫画对话框的读法就是从左往右(或从右往左)从上到下啊..<br>自由分镜漫画也遵循这个规律..你找准对话框的顺序就行了..","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/42/69/426934.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1504822","time":"2019-10-5 19:27","userId":"426934","userName":"火龙果汁","userSign":"","message":"对啊，我知道怎么读<img src=\"/im